title: Immune System - JJ Holistic Nutritional Therapy
description: The following is a sample of the protocol included in a preliminary client report. We recognize and highly appreciate the fact that every client is their person, with diverse medical, physical, cultural, and mental backgrounds. Therefore, this report should only be considered as a starting point or guideline Moreover, the client protocol is followed by a report on immune system health for your information. By utilizing lab and functional testing, you will be able to refine and personalize the program from your client.
